headline: onsemi and Innoscience Announce Plans to Collaborate to Speed Global Rollout of GaN Power Portfolio
summary: Collaboration would add high-volume, cost-optimized, worldwide GaN manufacturing for faster market deployment of energy-efficient power devicesSummary:onsemi announced it has signed a memorandum of understanding with Innoscience to explore expanding production of gallium nitride (GaN) power devices using Innoscience’s proven 200mm GaN-on-silicon process.
